SIMPLE: unlearned
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unlearned
<hw>Un*learn"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>learned</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not learned; untaught;
uneducated; ignorant; illiterate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not gained by study; not known.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not exhibiting learning; <as>as, <ex>unlearned</ex>
verses</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*learn"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*learn"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unleash</ent>⟦br⟧
